plot: Nombre Original: Ricky Gervais Live Show - AnimalsDirector: Ricky GervaisActores: Ricky GervaisAnimals is a stand-up show written and performed by the comedian Ricky Gervais. As the title suggests Gervais uses aspects of the animal kingdom as his central theme. The show toured in 2003 and is now available on DVD
